## SkillsUSA Theme & Client Values Alignment

### Connection to SkillsUSA Theme
This project demonstrates core SkillsUSA principles:
- **Teamwork** - Collaborative design and development between team members
- **Excellence** - Attention to detail in design, code quality, and user experience
- **Innovation** - Modern web technologies applied to create engaging user experience
- **Professional Communication** - Clear visual and narrative communication of client values

### Reflection of Aurora Coffee Roasters' Values
- **Quality** - Website design mirrors the premium nature of the product
- **Ethical Sourcing** - Company story section highlights commitment to ethical practices
- **Community** - Testimonials and subscription features foster customer connection
- **Craftsmanship** - Handcrafted design aesthetic reflects artisanal coffee roasting
- **Sustainability** - Focus on small-batch, intentional business practices

