## Credits & Third-Party Resources

- **W3Schools** - Primary reference for HTML, CSS, and JavaScript documentation and tutorials
- **Design Inspiration** - Specialty coffee industry branding standards
- **Typography** - System fonts for optimal web performance and accessibility
- **Imagery** - Mock product images created specifically for prototype demonstration

No external libraries, frameworks, or third-party design resources were incorporated. The website was built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to demonstrate foundational web development skills.

---

## Conclusion

Aurora Coffee Roasters' website successfully combines warm, welcoming design with modern web functionality. The site effectively communicates the brand's commitment to quality and ethical sourcing while providing visitors with an intuitive, engaging experience. This project showcases professional web development practices and collaborative teamwork aligned with SkillsUSA standards.
